---
// Hero.astro
---
<section class="relative pt-32 pb-20 lg:pt-48 lg:pb-32 overflow-hidden">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10 flex flex-col items-center text-center">
    
    <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-quaternary/30 border border-quaternary/50 text-secondary text-sm font-medium mb-8 fade-in">
      <span class="flex h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-tertiary"></span>
      Real Space Hub
    </div>

    <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-theme-white mb-6 fade-in delay-100 max-w-4xl leading-tight">
      Transforma tu inventario en una <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-linear-to-r from-theme-white to-secondary">máquina de ventas digital</span>
    </h1>

    <p class="mt-4 text-xl text-secondary max-w-2xl mb-10 fade-in delay-200">
      La plataforma todo-en-uno para desarrolladores inmobiliarios. Centraliza disponibilidad, cotizaciones y material comercial en una sola herramienta interactiva.
    </p>

    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center items-center w-full fade-in delay-300">
      <a href="#demo" class="w-full sm:w-auto px-8 py-4 bg-theme-white hover:bg-tertiary text-primary font-bold rounded-lg transition-all shadow-[0_0_40px_rgba(255,255,255,0.15)] hover:shadow-[0_0_60px_rgba(255,255,255,0.25)] transform hover:-translate-y-1">
        Agendar presentación
      </a>
      <a href="#showcase" class="w-full sm:w-auto px-8 py-4 bg-quaternary hover:bg-tertiary hover:text-primary border border-quaternary text-theme-white font-medium rounded-lg transition-all">
        Ver demo online
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

</section>
